<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="back-n">back <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bæk/    美 /bæk/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>背 (部)；脊柱：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He lay <strong>on</strong> his <strong>back</strong>. 
他仰面躺着。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>反面；背面：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She wrote down her ideas on the back of an envelope.
她把想法记在一个信封的背面。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>后面；后部：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>at the back of</strong> 
在…后面</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Two men were sitting <strong>in the back of</strong> the car. 
两名男子正坐在汽车的后排。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="back-to-back">back to back</h3>
<p>1.<strong>背靠背</strong>  </p></div>